data.description: This charming bi-level home sits on a  1-acre lot, boasting a 600 sq ft pole barn and a private backyard oasis. Entertain guests around the fire pit on the large brick patio, or enjoy the tranquility of the fenced-in yard with 3 gates for convenience. Inside, a delightful 3-season room off the kitchen beckons relaxation. The master bedroom features a  walk-in closet, while both full bathrooms showcase beautifully tiled showers. Modern amenities include 2023 new furnace, air conditioning and on-demand water heater. Commerical grade ejector pump . The kitchen has a center island and snack bar, complemented by hardwood floors throughout the kitchen and living room. Conveniently located just 8 miles from Pier Cove Park on the stunning shores of Lake Michigan.
